  Second, all surgical and nonsurgical procedures performed by oral-maxillofacial surgeons convey a high risk to HCP. Although some of these uncertainties and challenges will be resolved as the data regarding the virus and the disease improve, we all have some apprehension and reservations regarding delivering care in such an environment.
